      "content": "it's exactly that. i'm just a ghost. i go through the motions, i eat, i work, i come home... but what is the point? he was the one who made everything make sense. without him, i'm just carrying this massive weight for no reason. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. it's just more of the same. forever.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
